items.shortDescription: The Belvita Soft Baked Breakfast Biscuits are the right way to start your day. They give you energy in addition to being nutritious and delicious. This product is baked with hearty whole grains and provides the get up and go that you need in the morning. You can enjoy these biscuits with a serving of fruit and low-fat dairy as part of a balanced and wholesome breakfast. They are made with 11 grams of whole grain per 50-gram serving and contain no high fructose corn syrup, partially hydrogenated oils, artificial flavors or sweeteners. Keep these soft baked biscuits on hand for a savory banana bread appetite.They are a good source of B vitamins, which help convert food into energy, giving you the zip needed in order to be productive. This healthy item features a genuine banana flavor, good texture and offers 20 percent daily value of fiber and 7 grams of fat per serving.

items.name: Augason Farms Banana Chips 2 lbs 1 oz No. 10 Can
items.shortDescription: Augason Farms has over four decades of experience formulating and manufacturing delicious and healthy products in the food storage and emergency preparedness industry. Augason Farms Honey-Coated Banana Slices Long-Term Food Storage offers great taste and a healthy treat. Augason Farms Food Storage, 2 lb, Honey-Coated Banana Slices are dried by a low-heat process that removes moisture. The size of the fruit will shrink, which means there will be ample servings in each container. Augason Farms Honey-Coated Banana Slices are baked then cooked in vegetable and coconut oil with sugar and honey. They're sweet and delicious without any additives. These banana slices are packaged for long-term storage, and do not require refrigeration. They are great for emergency food storage, camping or everyday use.
items.longDescription: *Shelf life up to 10 years when unopened. Best when stored in a cool, dry and dark place at temperatures between 55° F and 70° F. Actual shelf life may vary based on individual storage conditions.
